title: [Keycard] Wrong keycard error shown if quickly tap the card on login flow several times
body:
# Problem
`Wrong keycard` error shown if quickly tap the card on login flow several times. Confuses user, since the card is valid.

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/28752642/57571416-8e7a6800-7416-11e9-95b7-83e25d25bab2.png)

## Steps


1. create account with keycard
1. login
1. logout
1. remove the card away from phone and select account to login the one you just created
1. enter PIN and wait for Hold the card prompt
1. quickly tap the card several times in a row
